layout.house_prompt: A hotel room with a bedroom and an en-suite bathroom. The bedroom has a bed with two nightstands on each side, a desk with a chair, and a TV mounted on the wall. The bathroom has a toilet, a sink, and a shower.

bedroom.text_description: A modern contemporary hotel bedroom with one queen bed centered on the headboard wall, two nightstands (one on each side of the bed), a work desk with a chair, and a TV mounted on the wall.

bathroom.text_description: A modern contemporary en-suite hotel bathroom with a toilet, a sink/vanity, and a walk-in shower.
